Class AccountListOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.FilterOptions
      • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.ListOptions
        • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.accounts.model.AccountListOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    @Preamble(description="Options to use when listing accounts.")
public class AccountListOptions
extends ListOptions
    Options to use when listing accounts.

    Note:

    • Filters:

      The list can be filtered server-side on some of the fields of an account.

      The following filters are currently supported:

      Server-side filters
      Field Tag Filters
      not equal to equal to greater than less than like in not in
      status TAG_FILTER_BY_STATUS • • •
      tier TAG_FILTER_BY_TIER •
      endMarket TAG_FILTER_BY_END_MARKET •
      country TAG_FILTER_BY_COUNTRY •
